// Trust Badges Section
---

<section id="trust-badges" class="py-8 md:py-16 px-6 bg-surface overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/components/home/TrustBadges.astro:trust-badges">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative group" data-ps="src/components/home/TrustBadges.astro:container">
